    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<b>Frameworks Pros and Cons&nbsp;</b>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<ul><li>Reasons&nbsp;</li><ul><li>Limited development resources&nbsp;</li><li>Limited pool of ideas&nbsp;</li></ul><li>Cons:</li><ul><li>Unknown code quality&nbsp;</li><li>Licensing cna be a hassle</li></ul><li>Pros:</li><ul><li>Larger feature set and expertise&nbsp;</li><li>Easier to get support, fixes, and ne developers&nbsp;</li></ul></ul>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<b>Golang Web Frameworks</b>"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "data": "<ul><li>Gorilla - large and not very performant&nbsp;<br></li><li>httprouter - a very fast router&nbsp;</li><li>Gin - quick and extensible&nbsp;</li><li>Echo - light and the quickest out there&nbsp;</li></ul>"
    },
